HEADWORD: Tinctorial
<hw>Tinc*to"ri*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tinctorius</ets>, from <ets>tinctor</ets> a dyer,
<ets>tingere</ets>, <ets>tinctum</ets>, to dye: cf. F.
<ets>tinctorial</ets>. See <er>Tinge</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or relating to
